{"tid":1558361,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"和理非全新戰線 - 全民帶棍日","createTime":"2019-09-10T12:18:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T23:06:03.000Z","uid":154702,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"856f009778c020280e2771b5cccffb39cd3be54a","tid":1558361,"uid":154702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T12:18:01.000Z","msg":"多得今日下午四點鐘呀乜sir 提醒<br />\n<br />\n原來政府帶頭鼓勵普通市民(包括休班警員)<br />\n可以帶棍出街四圍幫助人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但真.普通市民當然無咁幸福<br />\n<br />\n可以由納稅人課金提供日常武裝<br />\n<br />\n用黎打返其他納稅人<br />\n<br />\n不過大家唔駛氣餒<br />\n<br />\n坊間都好多棍狀物可以回應政府呼籲帶棍旁身<br />\n<br />\n幫助有需要既人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cskxbc7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCskxbc7.jpg&h=4d8d3e40&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zxzqwc8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZxzqwc8.jpg&h=96f785d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5632afde49b583a8515d90251fd40a61f073d5fe","tid":1558361,"uid":315793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T12:27:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/511608535553209/posts/2453691531344890?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F511608535553209%2Fposts%2F2453691531344890%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=fwl9YqZIxHA797AeyThx4fSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=fac7f89c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/511608535553209/posts/2453691531344890?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n【民陣：正申請 9.15 大遊行】<br />\n<br />\n社會及政治組織從業員工會晚上7時半在遮打花園舉行「反濫捕、抗威權集會」。民陣召集人岑子杰宣布，民陣正申請 9 月 15 日（周日）遊行，呼籲之前出過嚟的人再次上街。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係咪要再晒冷，嚟個百萬人奇蹟啊？<br />\n冇人提、冇人宣傳，一萬人都偷笑啦！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>星期日要人！<br />\n星期日要人！<br />\n星期日要人啊！！！</strong></span></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"3725eacce20de6b664b78214ec894a3dd46e7b06","tid":1558361,"uid":154702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:03:50.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"9abddcf0607428a5bee8101654ea7b2a14911eff","tid":1558361,"uid":154702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T22:27:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"26263e4f69c03c1ad17223bb3f64cbe150f895ef","tid":1558361,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T22:28:44.000Z","msg":"帶左差唔多三十年"},{"pid":"20161bc6061cb54408280b27de4eb8b5ac0956c0","tid":1558361,"uid":57856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T23:06:03.000Z","msg":"日日都要帶棍出街嫁啦<br />\n比恐怖份子襲擊都可以還下手，唔洗淨走"}]}